INSERT INTO `invitations` VALUES ('65', 'asdasd', 'asdasd', '67', '2018-05-01 14:26:31', '10', null, null, '<h1>A Special First Event</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>by&nbsp;<a href=\"http://localhost/one/blogs/page/a-special-first-event-59#\">Tricia Canilao</a></p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>&nbsp;Posted on April 28, 2018 11:31 AM</p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://localhost/one/uploads/blogs/blogs_201804281129281524886168.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" id=\"innercomp_m7oy1uc2imgimage\" src=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/7ee9b6_68f1c303cae14288a4f653ddb7ad5732~mv2_d_3008_4512_s_4_2.jpg/v1/fill/w_290,h_435,al_c,q_80,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01/7ee9b6_68f1c303cae14288a4f653ddb7ad5732~mv2_d_3008_4512_s_4_2.webp\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>March 23 was the very first&nbsp;Gift2Share event. It was the birthday celebration of my daughter, Ornella. I wasn&rsquo;t really sure how the website would be received, but talking to the charities we are supporting, they are excited. And the parents of the kids we invited, supported in one way or the other. And my 9 year old, and her 7 and 5 year old brothers, are thrilled at the fact that a part of the gifts will be going to charity. So keen are they to help out, that even Rocco, the 7 year old brother gave PHP200 to her fund raiser. And upon going home, we found gifts that were labeled &ldquo;for sharing&rdquo;. Kids and parents gave other forms of donations! And my two boys were joyous in saying &ldquo;Oh those gifts are for sharing!&rdquo;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" id=\"innercomp_mv6u1qodimgimage\" src=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/7ee9b6_d11eef90465f45448b741f543953695a~mv2_d_4512_3008_s_4_2.jpg/v1/fill/w_473,h_315,al_c,q_80,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01/7ee9b6_d11eef90465f45448b741f543953695a~mv2_d_4512_3008_s_4_2.webp\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>On behalf of my children, I&#39;d like to give a heartfelt thank you to everyone that came and supported the charity! And to He Cares, thank you for allowing us to make you our very first partner in this endeavour. We look forward to fostering a long term relationship with you. And to my children, thank you for always sparking new ideas that I would not have to courage nor awareness to begin if you were not in my life! And for understanding that as fortunate as you are in having so many people love you - that love can be furthered share even in the smallest of ways! Big things begin in the tiniest of hearts&hellip;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tricia Canilao</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Managing Director</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Gift2Share</p>\r\n', '1', 'invitations', null, 'asd@asd', 'asd', 'asd', 'asd', '123', 'martinezcederic@gmail.com,martinezcederic@gmail.com,martinezcederic@gmail.com,martinezcederic@gmail.com,martinezcederic@gmail.com,', '2018-05-08', '14:10:00', 'asd', 'asd', '123', 'asd');
