2_NBA_Finals\" title=\"2012 NBA Finals\">2012</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/2013_NBA_Finals\" title=\"2013 NBA Finals\">2013</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/2016_NBA_Finals\" title=\"2016 NBA Finals\">2016</a>)</li>\r\n				<li>3&times;&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bill_Russell_NBA_Finals_Most_Valuable_Player_Award\" title=\"Bill Russell NBA Finals Most Valuable Player Award\">NBA Finals MVP</a>&nbsp;(<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/2012_NBA_Finals\" title=\"2012 NBA Finals\">2012</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/2013_NBA_Finals\" title=\"2013 NBA Finals\">2013</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/2016_NBA_Finals\" title=\"2016 NBA Finals\">2016</a>)</li>\r\n				<li>4&times;&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/NBA_Most_Valuable_Player_Award\" title=\"NBA Most Valuable Player Award\">NBA Most Valuable Player</a>&nbsp;(<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/2008%E2%80%9309_NBA_season\" title=\"2008–09 NBA season\">2009</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/2009%E2%80%9310_NBA_season\" title=\"2009–10 NBA season\">2010</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/2011%E2%80%9312_NBA_season\" title=\"2011–12 NBA season\">2012</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/2012%E2%80%9313_NBA_season\" title=\"2012–13 NBA season\">2013</a>)</li>\r\n				<li>14&times;&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_NBA_All-Stars\" title=\"List of NBA All-Stars\">NBA All-Star</a>&nbsp;(<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/2005_NBA_All-Star_Game\" title=\"2005 NBA All-Star Game\">2005</a>&ndash;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/2018_NBA_All-Star_Game\" title=\"2018 NBA All-Star Game\">2018</a>)</li>\r\n				<li>3&times;&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/NBA_All-Star_Game_Most_Valuable_Player_Award\" title=\"NBA All-Star Game Most Valuable Player Award\">NBA All-Star Game MVP</a>&nbsp;(<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/2006_NBA_